Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.90,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,I will not let out of sight
Comment: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:36.87,Lyrics kanji,,0,0,0,,このともしびを 消しはしないと
